text: San Félix is a corregimiento in San Félix District, Chiriquí Province, Panama. It has a land area of and had a population of 2,972 as of 2010, giving it a population density of . Its population as of 1990 was 1,680; its population as of 2000 was 2,443. ==References== Category:Corregimientos of Chiriquí Province
